## 🚀 Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.9+
- NumPy 1.21+
- SciPy 1.7+
- Matplotlib 3.4+
- Jupyter Notebook (for exploration)

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/mangoluvzu.fam/TOE-2026-06-16-S25-OCTONION.git
cd TOE-2026-06-16-S25-OCTONION

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Install in development mode
python setup.py develop
